0.1.name: wordpress/google-syntax-highlighter-button
0.1.description: If you use the plugin "WP-Google Syntax Highlighter", you should install this plugin. WP-Google Syntax Highlighter is a plugin to highlight code. Our plugin provides a button for WP-Google Syntax Highlighter in TinyMCE editor. So, it becomes easy to use the Google Syntax Highlighter.
